*& Module status_0100 OUTPUT
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*MODULE status_0100 OUTPUT.
*  SET PF-STATUS 'ZSALV'.
** SET TITLEBAR 'xxx'.
*  PERFORM display_settings.
*  PERFORM display_alv_report.
*ENDMODULE.
